{"tid":1414414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沉默的代價","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:40:37.000Z","uid":90336,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3d465f6e212558d77da805699ebe70bffca480b9","tid":1414414,"uid":90336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:12:58.000Z","msg":"起初他們堅決不撤回條例，<br />\n因為我不反對條例，我不說話；<br />\n<br />\n接著他們使用槍械直接射擊示威者頭部，<br />\n因為我沒有身歷其境，我不說話；<br />\n<br />\n後來他們放縱黑社會襲擊市民，<br />\n因為我那天沒有去元朗，我繼續不說話；<br />\n<br />\n此後他們用催淚彈直接射入民居，<br />\n因為我住高層不受影響，我還是不說話；<br />\n<br />\n最後，他們奔向我來，<br />\n再也沒有人站起來為我說話了。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎補充，屌醒啲人同時記錄各大「暴行」"},{"pid":"051ab32f743bf009b419dd1af670f47c364c0b3f","tid":1414414,"uid":90336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:13:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88ace3bd9949754e24f52db8cb2eeb55cfd71569","tid":1414414,"uid":90336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:14:01.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"d74497538124e9e4cc144d36fe63f4a54bf7b9cd","tid":1414414,"uid":90336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:32:32.000Z","msg":"又推"},{"pid":"9e3a2575d1e48c60e0511b947ef9d794a5985afa","tid":1414414,"uid":286039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:54:36.000Z","msg":"話比更多人知"},{"pid":"72f1f7d58a42c6f96a669ea54f5dac03cec3ec4e","tid":1414414,"uid":90336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"推"}]}